    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new workshop for some execs at a firm. I need some solid advice on grooming and appearance to help them project an image of authority and professionalism during high-level boardroom meetings. Can you give me some general guidelines on hair, makeup, and overall presentation that work best for a high-stakes corporate setting?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
